the dollar turned mixed thursday against most 
key currencies as dealers assessed the impact of improved us 
trade figures for july 
gold prices declined republic national bank in new york quoted 
bullion at 41850 a troy ounce as of 4 pm edt down from 42980 
late wednesday 
